(48, 213, 'Offerta formativa', 'offerta-formativa', '', '<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify; background-color: transparent;">Il Master si contraddistingue per un <strong>approccio innovativo</strong> alla </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="line-height: normal;">formazione, che coniuga il rigore e la sistematicità della docenza </span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="line-height: normal;"> accademica con l''esperienza sul campo e lil pragmatismo della docenza </span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="line-height: normal;">aziendale e professionale.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"> </p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Il programma è articolato nei seguenti moduli didattici</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Parte I - Formazione Culturale</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000;">1. Introduzione alla crittografia moderna<br />2. Protocolli crittografici<br />3. Information Security Management and Legals<br />4. Computer security<br />5. Network security<br />6. Web security</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Parte II - Formazione professionale</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">7. Information Security Governance<br />8. Continuità Operativa e Gestione della Crisi<br />9. Informatica Legale, Privacy e Crimine Informatico<br />10. Fondamenti di Computer forensics<br />11. Critical Infrastructure Protection<br />12. Cyber Security nel sistema creditizio, Management in Incident Response<br />13. La Security nei sistemi SCADA<br />14. Mobile Security<br />15. Social Engineering and Intelligence for Cyber Security<br />16. Cloud Security</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Parte III - Specializzazioni</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Indirizzo 1: Incident Response and Computer Forensics Specialist<br />Indirizzo 2: Critical Infrastructure and Industrial Automation Protection Specialist</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"> </p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: left;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Sono previsti percorsi personalizzati per l’eventuale recupero di conoscenze di base relative al settore ICT e rendere omogenee le conoscenze di base nell’elettronica, l’informatica e le telecomunicazioni a seconda delle esigenze dei singoli partecipanti.  Verrà reso disponibile materiale didattico da discutere singolarmente con un docente di ogni settore a cui chiedere chiarimenti e spiegazioni.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;"> <br />PIANO DIDATTICO</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 1; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><img src="images/piano_didattico_2016-2017.gif" alt="piano didattico 2016 2017" /><map id="m_imagemap" name="m_imagemap">  \r\n<area shape="rect" coords="334,235,496,254" href="index.php/parte-iii-le-specializzazioni/2014-12-19-05-04-51/scada-protection-system" alt="" />\r\n \r\n<area shape="rect" coords=